# Lockfile intentionally untracked: the Windows-generated lock omits Linux-only
# optional native bindings (rolldown/@emnapi), which makes Cloudflare's strict
# `npm ci` fail. Without a lock, Cloudflare uses lenient `npm install` and
# resolves the correct platform deps at build time.
package-lock.json

